        "body": "Add several community browsers. Keychain/keyring names and profile paths were taken from the actual app binaries (`strings` on the framework/installer).\n\n### Changes\n- Chromium-family: Dia, ChatGPT Atlas (macOS); Comet (macOS + Windows); Whale (macOS / Windows / Linux)\n- Firefox-based: Zen, Floorp, Waterfox, LibreWolf (per-OS profile roots)\n- Map each to the existing Chromium / Firefox readers; add env overrides for the new Chromium browsers\n- Add darwin/linux/windows path tests, plus routing/vendor/env coverage\n\n### Notes\n- Comet: keychain `Comet Safe Storage`; Windows install brand `Perplexity\\Comet` (from the installer), macOS uses the bare `Comet` product dir\n- ChatGPT Atlas: inner Chromium app, keychain `ChatGPT Safe Storage`, data dir `com.openai.atlas.web`\n- Whale: keychain/keyring `Whale Safe Storage`\n- No Windows entry for Dia (Store/MSIX, path unverified) or Atlas (no Windows build); Opera Neon skipped (gated installer)\n\n### Verification\n- `make ci` (go test, golangci-lint, coverage ≥ 90%)\n- `GOOS=linux` and `GOOS=windows` builds",
